Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:05.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a fever and cough or sore throat... stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say 95% chance this is manufactured. Came out of a laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The source of the virus was traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to drug testing done at Gen-Sys Laboratories in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The lab technician now known as Patient Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was accidentally exposed to retrovirus ALZ-113....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,an Alzheimer's trial drug that was being tested on chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The infected chimps showed signs of erratic and aggressive behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that led to their escape from the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The now-famous incident on the Golden Gate Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a six-hour standoff with police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:36.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ended with the apes disappearing into Muir Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency rooms are being overwhelmed with patients showing signs...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of what's being dubbed "The Simian Flu."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The CDC is projecting a fatality toll...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ranging from 5 million to as many as 150 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:48.94,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the next 6 to 8 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone showing signs of a contagious illness will receive special treatment here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the airport's purpose-built quarantine center.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many of the new arrivals are children who have lost contact with their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mandatory quarantines have sparked civil unrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Families are being ripped apart. - Containment is not very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:09.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare your families. Know your evacuation route.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The survival rate is now approximately 1 in 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Violence erupted in the city center tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The third incident in as many days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:21.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Martial law has been declared in 28 nations including the U.S. and Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reactor is overheating. We can't stop a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:28.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a total collapse of anything resembling civilian order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the extremity of the Simian Flu crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all regular government functions have been suspended indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who aren't killed by the virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will probably die in the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, maybe this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be anyone left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:35.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Son, stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think before you act, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel bad, Blue Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scars make you strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come meet your new brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:18.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me think how far we've come, Maurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:25.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still think about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't know them like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only saw their bad side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:53.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good, bad... doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans destroyed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes fight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:13.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if they're really all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten winters now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:19.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last two... no sign of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bear wouldn't get me Blue Eyes. I'm quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shot him! I shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:34.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They shot Ash! Shot my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mean any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:49.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're apes, man. You think they understand what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do they look like just apes to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:07.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Dad. - Malcolm, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Dad? - Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put your guns down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You can't be serious. - Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Holy shit. - Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Okay, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- My bag! - Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The dam is pretty much intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It could probably start generating power for us within a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a problem. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:29.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shot him. I was scared. I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ. How many were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:33.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A lot. Like, 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- At least. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're not hearing what he's saying. They spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, Dreyfus, they did and it was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible? They're talking apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- With big-ass spears! - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:52.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly what you think you saw or heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you have to calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the virus, Ellie? Any chance of contagion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all genetically immune or we would've been dead a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You don't know that for sure. - She worked with the CDC. She knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What are we gonna do? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We need that power. - He could've killed us, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he kept us alive, so they could follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They find out where we are, and they kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you mean, "he"? - That's what we're trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was unlike anything you've ever seen before, and the leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- He was remarkable. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that what you thought? - It's what we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's what we all saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a word of this back at the colony, you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a word until we can figure out what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You gotta be kidding. - No, I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to create a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, pal? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I dropped my bag. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Was your sketchbook in there? - It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carver just told me we're not gonna tell anybody what happened up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Must attack them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before they attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many guns they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or why they came up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They shot your son, Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I follow Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They almost killed you, Ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:32.94,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We could lose all we've built...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:00.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will decide by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For years I was a prisoner in their lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They cut me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:26.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tortured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You freed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:34.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would do anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we must show strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will, Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:29.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coming through. Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hell of a lot more than eighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:22.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:55.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do not want war...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:04.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but will fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.49,0:24:09.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if we must.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.36,0:24:43.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:49.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.91,0:24:57.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:38.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.62,0:25:43.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you have to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.63,0:25:52.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:54.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.43,0:25:57.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please! We're all immune!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.87,0:26:02.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all immune, or we wouldn't still be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.81,0:26:04.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.78,0:26:06.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.90,0:26:09.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You knew they were out there! - What if they come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.45,0:26:11.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:14.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they come back... If they come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.24,0:26:17.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be sorry they ever did!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.95,0:26:23.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this city may not have the manpower it once did but it has the firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.13,0:26:27.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those stockpiles left behind by FEMA,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.78,0:26:30.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the National Guard, we have it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.01,0:26:33.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.43,0:26:37.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know why you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.64,0:26:41.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, too, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.85,0:26:45.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I recognize the trust you've all placed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:49.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been through hell together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.15,0:26:54.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you all know what we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:27:00.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost out of fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.71,0:27:03.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means no more power...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.33,0:27:06.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which means we could slip back to the way things were.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:11.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That dam up there was the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:15.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just had no idea they were up there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:18.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So, what do we do now? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.68,0:27:22.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We find another way...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.06,0:27:27.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because that power... is not just about keeping the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:32.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about giving us the tools to reconnect to the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.57,0:27:35.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To find out who else is out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.62,0:27:40.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that we can start to rebuild...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:44.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and reclaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:49.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the world we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.05,0:27:56.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.72,0:28:01.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no alternative power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.72,0:28:05.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That dam is the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.48,0:28:12.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, we fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.11,0:28:19.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're two weeks away from running out of fuel. Maybe three, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.49,0:28:22.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I know. - And once that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:26.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to go out there with a bullhorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.17,0:28:28.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and calm everybody down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.67,0:28:32.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need that power to get the radio transmitter working.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.76,0:28:36.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's our only chance of reaching the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.43,0:28:38.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find other survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.47,0:28:41.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There's not that many of us left.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.35,0:28:47.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We can't afford any more casualties. - We founded this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.60,0:28:49.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- you and I... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.98,0:28:54.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the idea that power would lead us back to the life we once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.36,0:28:57.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't stick together, maybe we can't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.11,0:28:59.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.66,0:29:05.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of losing what little I have is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.46,0:29:09.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.96,0:29:13.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. Give me three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.84,0:29:16.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to him. If it doesn't work, then we do it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.22,0:29:18.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what if it backfires? What if he gets violent?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.47,0:29:22.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, how do you know that he'll even understand you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.81,0:29:28.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's more than just an ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.15,0:29:32.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take some men up to Fort Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.82,0:29:38.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go through the armory. I'm gonna see what's still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.82,0:29:42.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three days. You're not back in three days we're going up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:45.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we're gonna kill every last one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.30,0:30:03.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carver is getting the trucks ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.97,0:30:07.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here with Foster and Kemp any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.43,0:30:10.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really taking Carver? I mean, he shot one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:13.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have any choice. He used to work at the water department.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.60,0:30:16.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one who knows how the dam works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:19.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.86,0:30:23.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what are you gonna do up there? What are you gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.33,0:30:28.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.25,0:30:31.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hope I catch him in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.80,0:30:38.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.92,0:30:41.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.43,0:30:44.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:47.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone over it in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.31,0:30:51.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I think if I don't at least try this...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.69,0:30:55.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there's gonna be a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.21,0:31:21.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you. What if someone gets hurt? You'll need me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.84,0:31:26.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.51,0:31:29.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I need you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.43,0:31:32.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Alexander to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.89,0:31:35.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.78,0:31:40.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Son, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.49,0:31:43.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm safer with you than I am down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.41,0:31:48.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.40,0:32:18.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one gets out of the trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:20.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.65,0:32:24.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not back in two hours, you get everyone back to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.90,0:32:27.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.09,0:35:32.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.39,0:35:37.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:40.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.48,0:35:43.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.73,0:35:48.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't come back." I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.36,0:35:50.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be here unless it were...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.28,0:35:52.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:59.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.41,0:36:04.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to show you something. It's not far.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.62,0:36:09.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Human lies! - No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.76,0:36:13.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.39,0:36:20.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I could just show you, then you'll understand. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.49,0:36:43.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.48,0:37:10.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we used to call a "small hydro."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.36,0:37:13.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was built to service areas to the north of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.28,0:37:16.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we've been working to reroute the power lines to the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.41,0:37:19.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because the city used to run off nuclear power, but that ran out years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:21.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, we've been using diesel generators and gasifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.95,0:37:24.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we can just get this dam working...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.87,0:37:29.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then we have a shot at restoring limited power.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.30,0:37:39.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is any of this making any sense to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.35,0:37:43.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The... lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.39,0:37:45.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.23,0:37:47.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.65,0:37:53.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home and I don't want to take it away from you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.19,0:37:57.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can let us do our work here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.85,0:38:00.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You brought others?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.16,0:38:06.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.50,0:38:10.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a threat. If I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.67,0:38:13.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I guess you can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.19,0:38:40.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.74,0:38:45.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait, wait, wait! - Stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.96,0:38:59.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to give them our guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.55,0:39:03.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:07.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What does that mean? - We can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.03,0:39:25.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they get power, they'll be more dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:27.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.37,0:39:29.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They seem desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:33.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we make them go, they'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.25,0:39:35.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.38,0:39:39.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll destroy them while they're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.84,0:39:43.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And how many apes will die?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.35,0:39:48.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have one chance for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.02,0:39:52.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let them do their human work. Then they'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.23,0:39:56.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human work?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:02.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human work.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.91,0:40:07.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human work.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:09.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human work!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.41,0:40:48.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba say...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.08,0:40:51.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes should hate humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.33,0:40:52.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.70,0:40:55.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From humans Koba learned hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.17,0:40:57.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.81,0:41:14.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You need to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.64,0:41:16.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.57,0:41:19.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was brave, what you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.11,0:41:30.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm. I know everyone's depending on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.74,0:41:34.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that. I don't care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.33,0:41:37.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.58,0:41:43.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He saw things that no kid should see, and I'm not letting us go back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:49.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.23,0:42:02.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been trying to get closer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.40,0:42:04.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.61,0:42:06.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.66,0:42:13.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know the scary thing about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.87,0:42:17.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need power, lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.08,0:42:20.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heat. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.00,0:42:23.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, pal. - That's their advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.38,0:42:26.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes them stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.05,0:42:29.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, I'm thinking one of us should stand guard tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.88,0:42:31.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With what? They took our guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.84,0:42:33.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they wanted us dead, we would be dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:37.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're just taking their time. They killed off half the planet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:39.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.14,0:42:41.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What? - You can't honestly blame the apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.81,0:42:45.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell else am I going to blame? It was the Simian Flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.60,0:42:47.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a virus created by scientists in a lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.82,0:42:50.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The chimps they were testing on didn't have a say in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.31,0:42:52.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the hippie-dippie bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.49,0:42:56.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me you don't get sick to your stomach at the sight of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.83,0:43:02.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Didn't you have a little girl? - Carver, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.33,0:43:03.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- How did she die? - That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.87,0:43:05.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or your wife, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.21,0:43:08.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carver, you better shut up before I kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.84,0:43:13.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.76,0:43:18.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.10,0:43:25.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.79,0:43:48.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sound sick... You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.34,0:43:52.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just need rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:03.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You worry about the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.91,0:45:04.94,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Koba?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.04,0:45:09.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.00,0:45:13.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Said he was going hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.85,0:45:23.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, humans below!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.11,0:45:38.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.32,0:45:41.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar trusts humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.53,0:45:44.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.16,0:45:48.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Most of the arsenal seems functional. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.12,0:45:50.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're testing them out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.05,0:46:39.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.72,0:46:44.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you move! Don't move, do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.01,0:46:49.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terry! Terry, get in here, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.82,0:46:58.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.57,0:47:03.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.66,0:47:05.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.83,0:47:09.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Should we shoot him? - Maybe. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.25,0:47:15.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are one ugly son of a bitch, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.73,0:47:36.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.40,0:47:41.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, I think he's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.07,0:47:44.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must have gotten separated from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.57,0:47:49.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lost? Trying to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.78,0:47:52.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Get out of here, stupid monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.62,0:47:55.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Go on. You heard him. Go! - Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.09,0:48:06.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough guns here to kill every ape...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.43,0:48:07.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Must warn Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.01,0:48:10.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what humans are really doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.95,0:48:32.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta clear this blockage.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.04,0:48:40.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.63,0:48:46.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.47,0:48:53.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.98,0:49:00.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.49,0:49:06.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.95,0:49:17.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I have you and your dad, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.05,0:49:25.46,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.26,0:49:28.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you got that straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.02,0:49:42.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the wire we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.61,0:49:45.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.25,0:49:50.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.79,0:49:58.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Dad! - Malcolm!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.84,0:50:05.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm! Malcolm!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.63,0:50:06.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.22,0:50:08.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Carver.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.37,0:50:33.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.70,0:50:36.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Leave it there. - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.12,0:50:40.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.29,0:50:44.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let go. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.26,0:50:57.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.10,0:51:02.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saved our lives. We've got a lot of debris to clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.73,0:51:06.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We might need a bit more time. - How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.06,0:51:45.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.16,0:51:53.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.76,0:51:56.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.25,0:52:01.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.17,0:52:11.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.42,0:52:13.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.88,0:52:21.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey! I'll kill you! - Carver, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.99,0:52:28.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't! Caesar, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.98,0:52:30.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.71,0:52:49.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Said no guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.88,0:52:54.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- No, don't. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.25,0:53:28.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.13,0:53:39.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.39,0:54:25.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we screwed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.69,0:54:30.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.81,0:54:34.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, where are you going? Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.37,0:54:43.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please, I just need to speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.87,0:54:49.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. That was all my fault. But I will make him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.58,0:54:52.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.09,0:54:57.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You should not be here. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.72,0:55:00.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.43,0:55:06.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.82,0:55:10.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long has she been this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.78,0:55:20.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.86,0:55:23.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Antibiotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.03,0:55:27.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.71,0:55:32.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.71,0:55:37.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.30,0:55:41.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But believe me... we are not all like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:43.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.55,0:55:47.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.94,0:56:17.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One day.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.30,0:56:23.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stay one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.24,0:56:27.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We might need more time. - One day!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.09,0:56:34.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.65,0:56:41.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will not help!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.99,0:56:45.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- This is bullshit, man! - Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.95,0:56:48.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move! That's enough. Come on, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.79,0:56:51.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.63,0:56:58.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.38,0:57:02.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.30,0:57:08.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.82,0:57:25.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.99,0:57:33.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just came from the city. Humans very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.45,0:57:35.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.17,0:57:42.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.30,0:57:52.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Alex. This relay's busted. See if there's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.10,0:57:53.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.58,0:58:16.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.17,0:58:23.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.01,0:58:29.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, no, no, don't! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.31,0:58:40.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where Caesar? Want Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.15,0:58:42.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.12,0:59:02.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans attack your sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.46,0:59:06.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You let them stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.30,0:59:12.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put apes in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.56,0:59:17.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar love humans more...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.77,0:59:19.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,than apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.65,0:59:23.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More than your...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.98,0:59:26.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sons.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.99,1:00:14.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.45,1:00:17.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.29,1:00:20.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kill... ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.15,1:00:51.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.27,1:01:28.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.02,1:01:31.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to listen...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.41,1:01:47.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell Caesar about the guns we found?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.04,1:01:53.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.35,1:02:08.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your father doesn't trust me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.52,1:02:12.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.73,1:02:15.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His love for humans...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.03,1:02:17.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,makes him blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.99,1:02:20.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.66,1:02:25.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they are here...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.62,1:02:31.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I fear for Caesar's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.93,1:03:22.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.54,1:03:48.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:52.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch. Watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.33,1:03:54.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"It was Friday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.96,1:03:57.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A real nice afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.80,1:03:59.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.72,1:04:05.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were hanging...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.68,1:04:08.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were hanging out...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.14,1:04:11.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at this kegger down at the swimming hole."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.06,1:04:15.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.32,1:04:19.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.86,1:04:24.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You can read?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.92,1:04:36.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.51,1:04:41.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.06,1:04:51.46,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you? I thought we told you to go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.56,1:04:53.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.14,1:04:55.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.03,1:05:00.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- He understood that, didn't he? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.86,1:05:03.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.78,1:05:05.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.87,1:05:10.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.70,1:05:14.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Whoa, whoa, whoa. - Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.42,1:05:19.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I think he likes you. - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.55,1:05:21.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.30,1:05:25.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want a drink, fugly?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.34,1:05:27.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, give him some.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.60,1:05:30.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give him some, man. See what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.02,1:05:36.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. Whoa, hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.06,1:05:40.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.94,1:05:42.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.91,1:05:49.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- That's good, huh? - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.20,1:05:54.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.96,1:05:56.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Easy. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.67,1:05:57.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Easy. - Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.96,1:05:59.46,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.76,1:06:50.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm! Malcolm!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.93,1:06:53.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.90,1:08:33.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.66,1:08:39.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least here it did. We'll know when we get back to the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.29,1:08:47.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.99,1:09:14.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.66,1:09:17.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.12,1:10:06.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The... lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.49,1:10:38.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.44,1:11:18.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.43,1:12:30.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.69,1:12:35.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.41,1:12:53.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans kill Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.75,1:13:00.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn ape home!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.73,1:13:13.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.06,1:13:18.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes must attack human city!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.44,1:13:20.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.99,1:13:25.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come, fight for Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.58,1:13:30.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Females and young stay in woods...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.70,1:13:32.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We go to the city!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.09,1:13:44.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will avenge your father's death!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.11,1:14:00.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie! Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.30,1:15:53.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is San Francisco attempting contact. If anyone is receiving this message...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.30,1:15:57.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we ask that you identify yourself and your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.82,1:16:11.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.67,1:16:29.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you are receiving this signal, please state your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.80,1:16:33.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat. This is San Francisco attempting to establish contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.85,1:16:35.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you are receiving this signal
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.14,1:16:38.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please state your identity and your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.43,1:16:42.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it? - The apes attacked the armory, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.98,1:16:49.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sound the alarm! Sound the alarm!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.68,1:17:27.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep them off the walls! Keep them off the walls!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.24,1:17:32.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Get into position.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.70,1:17:38.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You ready? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.16,1:17:39.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.58,1:17:42.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.54,1:17:45.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are survivors!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.75,1:17:48.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, they may have got their hands on some of our guns...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.21,1:17:51.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that does not make them men.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.26,1:17:54.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are animals! We will push them back!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.18,1:17:57.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them down!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.10,1:18:01.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they will not get through these doors!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.13,1:18:41.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There! California Street!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.58,1:20:30.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me the rocket launcher!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.67,1:22:46.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have a beacon marking our location. Please, we need help. We are under attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.09,1:22:48.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,San Francisco. Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.85,1:22:51.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello? - Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.37,1:23:20.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans escaping! Capture them!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.48,1:23:45.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We must be getting close.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.91,1:23:53.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I see it. It's down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.12,1:23:58.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.10,1:24:16.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God. Malcolm!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.98,1:24:19.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie, help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.78,1:24:33.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.99,1:24:35.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,son...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.91,1:24:40.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.21,1:24:42.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,family...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.38,1:24:48.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.39,1:24:54.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.06,1:25:07.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to speak. You need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.91,1:25:18.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.38,1:25:31.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- He's lost a lot of blood. - Is he going to make it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.84,1:25:33.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.89,1:25:37.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Carver get the gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.43,1:25:40.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Why would he do this? - Ape...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.77,1:25:44.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.02,1:25:48.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.03,1:25:51.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,did...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.28,1:25:54.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.25,1:26:03.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.52,1:26:26.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Followed the humans here. Hiding everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.86,1:26:29.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We must catch them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.88,1:26:50.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kill him. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.05,1:26:58.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead Ash...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.68,1:27:01.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,make humans pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.98,1:27:08.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar wouldn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.64,1:27:50.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar gone...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.98,1:27:57.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes follow...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.24,1:28:01.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.89,1:28:26.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, my God. Look, the colony's on fire. - Where are we going to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.35,1:28:28.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.73,1:28:40.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Is this it? Are we close? - Where is he taking us?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.57,1:28:44.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.71,1:28:56.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand. What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.13,1:28:57.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. We just need a place to hide him
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.96,1:29:00.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,until we find out what's going on at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.72,1:29:06.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go move the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.06,1:29:12.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.56,1:29:15.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.40,1:29:21.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.28,1:29:23.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.16,1:29:32.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to operate. I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.62,1:29:34.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a surgical kit back at the place, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.42,1:29:35.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.80,1:29:41.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's not safe. - He's the only one that can stop this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.26,1:29:46.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.30,1:29:49.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You ape prisoner now!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.06,1:29:54.40,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will know life in cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.10,1:29:58.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More humans out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.32,1:30:01.40,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.26,1:30:22.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maurice...?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.97,1:30:25.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba said...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.59,1:30:28.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we're too loyal to your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.02,1:30:35.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.39,1:31:55.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.67,1:33:07.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.63,1:33:10.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.89,1:33:15.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.19,1:33:28.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.85,1:33:30.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.76,1:33:58.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your... mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.06,1:34:01.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.60,1:34:04.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.27,1:34:07.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.91,1:34:17.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.37,1:34:18.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.70,1:34:24.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not human.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.42,1:34:30.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.88,1:34:35.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.59,1:34:37.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.72,1:34:40.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.72,1:34:44.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to do this now.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.86,1:34:49.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Son.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.14,1:35:26.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.10,1:35:30.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.15,1:35:33.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's very strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.58,1:35:45.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.82,1:36:20.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.78,1:36:22.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.95,1:36:25.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.25,1:36:31.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.29,1:36:33.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,am to blame.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.13,1:36:37.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Koba betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.67,1:36:39.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.13,1:36:43.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chose to trust him...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.43,1:36:48.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because he is ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.69,1:36:51.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always think...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.60,1:36:55.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ape better than human.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.78,1:37:00.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.66,1:37:06.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how much like them we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.54,1:37:13.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where Koba now?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.79,1:37:17.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the human tower...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.26,1:37:20.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loyal apes around him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.55,1:37:24.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And those who not follow?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.55,1:37:26.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.77,1:37:29.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maurice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.81,1:37:31.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.48,1:37:38.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba killed Ash.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.24,1:37:46.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fear makes others follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.83,1:37:51.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when they see you alive...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.17,1:37:55.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They will turn from Koba.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.25,1:37:57.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I am weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.92,1:38:04.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape always seek strongest branch.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.35,1:38:11.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must do something to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.40,1:38:23.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.78,1:38:30.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.96,1:39:23.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.69,1:41:43.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.86,1:41:46.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.65,1:41:49.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apple. Apple.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.07,1:41:52.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.82,1:41:56.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Home. Home.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.20,1:42:00.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.33,1:42:02.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.33,1:42:08.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home. Your home.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.59,1:42:12.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.43,1:42:15.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.08,1:42:42.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I didn't mean to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.88,1:42:48.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.34,1:42:57.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.52,1:43:03.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.89,1:43:07.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the video.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.27,1:43:13.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.49,1:43:18.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.65,1:43:50.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They need to get to the tower without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.65,1:43:53.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take him through the subway.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.40,1:43:55.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.11,1:43:58.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba sent for the females and young.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.53,1:44:01.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.41,1:44:03.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother too.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.25,1:44:07.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Must go. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.80,1:44:19.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.87,1:44:34.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there? If you're human, you better say so!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.19,1:44:37.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's Malcolm! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.57,1:44:40.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stairs... take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.99,1:44:44.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll bring you around and up under the street, okay? Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.41,1:44:49.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.17,1:44:52.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.05,1:45:01.04,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm coming out!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.14,1:45:03.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.66,1:45:23.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look who I found.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.66,1:45:25.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know if you'd made it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.91,1:45:27.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.12,1:45:30.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We're gonna turn all this around.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.42,1:45:34.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you mean? What's going on? - The apes. They're all over the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.25,1:45:37.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I lost the signal. It dropped out. - Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.30,1:45:39.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.18,1:45:43.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-4. Five-pound blocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.05,1:45:46.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just started setting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.35,1:45:49.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna take down the whole tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.02,1:45:53.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blast them all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.94,1:45:56.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.60,1:46:37.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is San Francisco attempting contact. If anyone is receiving this...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.82,1:46:41.40,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we ask that you identify yourself and your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.99,1:46:46.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.75,1:46:49.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone is receiving this, we ask that you identify yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.66,1:46:51.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.84,1:47:02.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is San Francisco attempting contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.12,1:47:05.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone is receiving this we ask that you identify yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.25,1:47:06.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and your location.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.01,1:47:11.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.31,1:47:21.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone is receiving this, we ask that you identify yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.28,1:47:23.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and your location. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.28,1:47:28.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dreyfus.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.38,1:47:34.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Can anybody hear me? - Werner.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.42,1:47:40.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't let you do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.63,1:47:43.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to give him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.67,1:47:49.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to give him some time. He's up there right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.39,1:47:53.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's up there?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.00,1:48:36.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar has no place here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.56,1:48:40.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes follow...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.73,1:48:42.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.99,1:48:48.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Koba...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.41,1:48:50.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to war.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.74,1:48:53.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes win war!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.95,1:48:58.75,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apes together strong!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.42,1:49:05.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.30,1:49:08.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.43,1:49:15.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba weaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.81,1:50:06.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your fucking mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.15,1:50:10.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've seen things. I've seen the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.99,1:50:13.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They want what we want, to survive. They don't want a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.92,1:50:17.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're animals! They attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.11,1:50:20.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because they thought we attacked them. They think that he's dead, but he's not...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.15,1:50:24.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, Finney! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.36,1:50:49.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trusted Koba like brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.78,1:50:53.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar brother to human!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.53,1:50:58.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba fight for ape!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.54,1:51:00.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free ape!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.87,1:51:04.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kill ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.29,1:51:06.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba fight for Koba.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.72,1:51:16.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koba...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.59,1:51:20.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,belong in cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.04,1:52:10.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know how this must sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.61,1:52:12.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have any...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.32,1:52:22.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think stopping me will matter? They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.79,1:52:26.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we made contact with a military base up north.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.16,1:52:29.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're already on their way!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.50,1:52:31.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.85,1:52:38.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dreyfus! What are you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.14,1:52:50.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving the human race.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.15,1:52:51.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.46,1:55:14.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.50,1:55:16.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not kill...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.34,1:55:19.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.15,1:55:46.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.16,1:55:50.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.83,1:55:55.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.74,1:57:11.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.09,1:57:31.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.43,1:57:34.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They made contact. Other people are coming. Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.72,1:57:37.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to leave now. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.57,1:57:41.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go, it'll be all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.48,1:57:43.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,War...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.27,1:57:45.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has already...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.48,1:57:48.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.61,1:57:52.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ape started war.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.49,1:57:57.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And human...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.62,1:58:03.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human will not forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.88,1:58:09.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must go...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.97,1:58:14.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,before fighting begins.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.51,1:58:17.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.81,1:58:23.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.48,1:58:30.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.74,1:58:36.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did, too.
